a)There is a Make Accusation button in the GUI on the bottom right.
b)There is a window to the right of the board to enter accusation.
c)There are directions on the top of the window that specifies when does
the player enter a person, weapon, and room.
d)The console says invalid entry when an input does not relate to the game.
e)Once the player enters the accusation phase, the player can input the 
player, weapon, and room. There will be a confirmation message. 

